      <title>力拓铜业老板表示建造矿山比购买更好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/rio-tinto-copper-boss-says-building-mines-is-better-than-buying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[力拓集团的铜业负责人表示，他认为建设矿山比购买现有资产更有价值——这些评论可能会让预计出现另一波矿业交易的行业观察家感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/rio-tinto-copper-boss-says-building-mines-is-better-than-buying</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 20:09:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
